"Authentication Failed. Access Denied.“
Role-Based Access: 
❑ If the role is "Admin":  The system will display: "Full Access“
❑ If the role is "Guest":   The system will display: "Limited Access“
❑ For any other role (e.g., "User," "Manager"): The system will display: "No Access"
